data.description: JUST REDUCED! PUBLIC OPEN HOUSE SUNDAY FROM 2-4. Charming move-in ready home with an assumable FHA loan at 3.25%! Located on a quiet cul de sac in the highly sought after neighborhood of Wexhurst. Beautiful new flooring throughout the first floor. An over-sized great room showcases a beautiful wood burning fireplace and inviting bay window. The gourmet eat-in kitchen features quartz countertops, gas stove, soft close cabinets and an amazing custom pantry. A formal dining room, laundry room and half bath complete the first floor. Upstairs you will find a large master suite with a gorgeous bay window, large walk-in closet, double vanity and tub/shower. There are also two large bedrooms and a recently updated shared bath. An expansive bonus room can easily become a fourth bedroom with the addition of a closet. There is great storage throughout including attic storage and a large walk-in closet under the stairs. A great deck overlooks a fully fenced-in backyard. This is truly an amazing home with an amazing interest rate!
